text: Adrian Fontes (born 1969/1970) is an American politician, election official, veteran, and attorney. He is the Secretary of State of Arizona since 2023. Fontes was the Maricopa County Recorder from 2017 until 2021. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Arizona Category:Lawyers from Arizona Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
